  "title": "BTW - Ore Breaking",
  "description": "An ore mining overhaul to increase mining experience",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://cf.way2muchnoise.eu/versions/1161229.svg\" alt=\"title\" width=\"135\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<div><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/NeoForge-lime?style=plastic&amp;link=https%3A%2F%2Fneoforged.net%2F\" alt=\"Static Badge\" /></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">This mod replace block disintegration of all ores with an ore cluster</span></p>\n<p><br /><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/BTW%20Ores/gif.gif?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"994\" height=\"747\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">An ore cluster can be regenerated by placing around it some specific rocks (based on type of cluster)</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">To see more information about it , you just need to use an <strong>Ore Cluster Scanner</strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/BTW%20Ores/scanner.gif?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"994\" height=\"826\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Compatibility/customization</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Everything can be configured using a datapack</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">This mod is heavly inspired by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/better-than-wolves\">BetterThanWolves</a> mod but completly recreated from scratch</span></p>",
